## src/app/app.component.css

```css
/* Estilos del Side Drawer con colores pasteles */

@import '~@nativescript/theme/css/core.css';
@import '~@nativescript/theme/css/default.css';

/* Header del drawer */
.sidedrawer-header {
    background-color: #D4A5FF; /* Lavanda pastel medio */
    padding: 30 20;
}

.sidedrawer-header-brand {
    font-size: 24;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    text-align: center;
}

.sidedrawer-header-subtitle {
    font-size: 12;
    color: #F5F5F5;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 5;
}

/* Contenido del drawer */
.sidedrawer-content {
    background-color: #FAF3F0; /* Beige pastel muy suave */
    padding-top: 10;
}

.sidedrawer-list-item {
    padding: 16 20;
    margin: 4 8;
    border-radius: 10;
}

.sidedrawer-list-item.selected {
    background-color: #E8D5FF; /* Lavanda pastel claro */
}

.sidedrawer-list-item-icon {
    font-size: 22;
    margin-right: 15;
    color: #6B4C9A; /* P√∫rpura oscuro suave */
    vertical-align: center;
}

.sidedrawer-list-item-text {
    font-size: 16;
    color: #5D4E6D;
    vertical-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
}

.sidedrawer-list-item.selected .sidedrawer-list-item-text {
    color: #6B4C9A;
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Action Bar */
.action-bar {
    background-color: #D4A5FF; /* Lavanda pastel medio */
    color: #FFFFFF;
}
```

